  "detailed_description": "This is a vampire survivor game, including tower defense, survival, and light meat pigeon gameplay. Through a variety of weapons and skills, avoid and eliminate beasts and monsters, and finally eliminate the abyssal demons and escape. Enjoy yourself!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemy introduction</h2>1. Randomly generated monsters, the monsters are different during the day and night!<br>2. Bosses are randomly generated. There are many types of bosses, each with their own skills. New bosses will be gradually added as the version changes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/d9012cc1ead74bb42710145b35e6130c.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=160 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/d9012cc1ead74bb42710145b35e6130c.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/f8ae7fa4c5746713431e56214faa77d8.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/f8ae7fa4c5746713431e56214faa77d8.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/1541a60d898fd28213767ae018b757b2.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/1541a60d898fd28213767ae018b757b2.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/46e8bd3cf17d3b15b56ec890c5a1ed1a.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/46e8bd3cf17d3b15b56ec890c5a1ed1a.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character introduction</h2>1. Multiple characters can be selected, and each character has a unique skill. Using this skill well can increase your chances of survival! New characters will be gradually added as the version changes!<br>2. Players can destroy enemies by creating attack methods such as rotating knife towers, arrow towers, and magic towers, and gain experience to upgrade these weapons!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/0833d02a92a76eec349350c3fcae1224.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/0833d02a92a76eec349350c3fcae1224.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/bc1d25fb041b4709fd0373264209b309.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/bc1d25fb041b4709fd0373264209b309.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/0bd0e4d63d845f6f8f622683522ee1b8.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/0bd0e4d63d845f6f8f622683522ee1b8.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/8b8767f2b2539d6b0388b4f828b6a2cb.poster.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/8b8767f2b2539d6b0388b4f828b6a2cb.webm?t=1689351593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2>1. Obtain experience points by destroying monsters, 3 skill cards will appear randomly, choose one of them to enhance your character!<br>2. There are a variety of skill cards, such as upgrading the rotating knife tower, arrow tower, magic tower, etc., as well as its own attack auxiliary skills!<br>3. The boss will be different every time you encounter it, and the level will be cleared only by destroying all the bosses!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/19b1ca11189938b40efb8ce027f96ce2.avif?t=1689351593\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444940/extras/4ad47ab9ea68ebd6249b03144636625b.avif?t=1689351593\" width=600 height=280 /></span>",
